        </p>
         <div class="special-features">
     <span class="feature-tag">🌰 Ceviz Dolgulu</span>
      <span class="feature-tag gold">📜 Geleneksel Tarif</span>
         <span class="feature-tag">🍯 Hafif Şerbet</span>
                <span class="feature-tag">⭐ Yöresel</span>
  </div>
           <div class="price-container">
  <span class="price-badge special">900 ₺</span>
        </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>